sub_title: Label Manager at 2-Dutch Records, Dutch Master Works & Skink Records
summary:
Hey! 

My name is Marijn & I work at The Music Group / 2-Dutch as a label manager for the record labels 2Dutch Records, Dutch Master Works and Skink Records. After finishing my commercial economics degree, with a focus on International Events, Music & Entertainment (CE-IEMES) at Fontys ACI in Tilburg I started here, which made my dream come true: find a job in the dance industry!

Dance music is my biggest passion, however, sports & gaming follow closely. Therefore, I'm very thankful to be employed within one of these beautiful industries!
